# C4.github.io

Documentation for following Years to help maintain the website.

Link: https://cornellcollegec4club.github.io/C4.github.io/

\*\*Designed and Updated by Ethan Kupka as of Sept.2022-May.2023

-About the project:
This project is mainly a static website for the computer science club at Cornell College.
Mainly Used vanilla JS, bootstrap, googleSheets, html, sass, and css.
If you want to mess around with it make a copy of the project and do that rather chang the main code.

Four main sections in the project:
-blogPosts File (Handles the html pages for blog posts, has a file for images used by those html files)
-images file (Handles the general images used by the three main html files of website and a file for not in use images)
-styles file (Handles the style of html pages)
-main html files and main js file

